A cyberpunk digital landscape showing a vast glowing tree structure made of neon circuits and data streams, its branches extending into a dark void filled with floating translucent cubes representing connected services. The tree's roots dig deep into a luminous grid floor pulsing with electric blue and magenta energy. Each branch terminus connects to hovering geometric containers emitting soft holographic light, suggesting discovered resources in a digital realm. The atmosphere is moody with fog-like data particles drifting through the scene, rain streaking down, and distant towering server monoliths silhouetted against a purple-orange sky. The perspective is from below looking up into the sprawling canopy of connections.
